<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>M-FLOATING-AI · Demo · HoloLake</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #f0f2ff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .demo-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 48px 40px;
      max-width: 480px;
      width: 90%;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .hint {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      background: #f0f2ff;
      color: #667eea;
      padding: 8px 18px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
  </style>
  <script src="api-client.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="demo-card">
    <h1>🍼 HoloLake AI 悬浮球</h1>
    <p>M-FLOATING-AI · Phase 1 · DEV-004 之之 × 秋秋</p>
    <p>点击右下角的悬浮球，或使用快捷键 <strong>Cmd/Ctrl+K</strong> 唤出对话框。</p>
    <div class="hint">⌘ / Ctrl + K 唤出</div>
  </div>

  <!-- 注入悬浮球 -->
  <script src="./floating-ball.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
